{"tid":789820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣文化入侵】 做雞都講環保 KFC明起全線停供膠飲管杯蓋","createTime":"2018-08-22T13:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T01:10:53.000Z","uid":202698,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f53c69fb0f0178e455e2f1eae8f5b3510140f9e0","tid":789820,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180822/s00001/cda53b49d75b81285a2a296bb2785894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180822%2Fs00001%2Fcda53b49d75b81285a2a296bb2785894.jpg&h=d402fb21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球連鎖快餐店，正陸續停止供應塑膠飲管及杯蓋等。肯德基香港今日宣佈，<span style=\"color: red;\">明日（23日）起，港澳全線71間分店，均停止供應塑膠飲管及杯蓋</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n肯德基香港指，上月16日起已於全港9間門市試行，顧客堂食購買指定凍飲時，店員不會主動提供杯蓋與飲管，得到市民正面回應。"},{"pid":"10f54bdb8f5fe965bee9ffd0baffd1877fdd971f","tid":789820,"uid":36551,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舖面又污糟，啲雞又越黎越瘦越黎越難食，而家連杯蓋都唔撚俾咁反智，狗都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173049f7abc527ea34b8bb7de3f9bdd4f932cd08","tid":789820,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"杯蓋都唔俾係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6ab5964cc88bd1cb8f1e34f5d4ee6e0fa75de5","tid":789820,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173049f7abc527ea34b8bb7de3f9bdd4f932cd08","tid":789820,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"杯蓋都唔俾係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"攞走唔畀杯蓋嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class